Given an integer array nums, handle multiple queries where you need to calculate the sum of the elements between index left and right (inclusive).

Java:
class NumArray {
    int[] p;
    public NumArray(int[] a) {
        int n=a.length;
        p=new int[n+1];
        for(int i=0;i<n;i++) p[i+1]=p[i]+a[i];
    }
    public int sumRange(int l,int r) {
        return p[r+1]-p[l];
    }
}

Python:
class NumArray:

    def __init__(self,a):
        self.p=[0]
        for x in a:
            self.p.append(self.p[-1]+x)

    def sumRange(self,l,r):
        return self.p[r+1]-self.p[l]
